Question: Explain to your grandmother how to use her smartphone to find new restaurant in her area.
Answer:
Grandma, your new smartphone is a great tool for you to use to explore the world easier. Unfortunately, it can be very complicated because you are not used to technology. Therefore, you should look in the user guide to see if there is a voice-activated search feature. If there is not, you should use it to call me and I will Google the restaurant for you.